<bibRefCitation author="Knight-Jones" pageId="3" pageNumber="50" refString="Knight-Jones, P. &amp; Fordy, M. R. (1979) Setal structure, functions and interrelationships in Spirorbidae (Polychaeta: Sedentaria). Zoologica Scripta, 8, 119 - 138." type="journal article" year="1979">
